Tortall Immortals quiz
[INS::INS]
Fun Trivia

This is a quiz on the immortals in the "Tortall" books by Tamora Pierce. Enjoy!

Average score for this quiz is 8 / 10. Difficulty: Easy. Played 819 times. As of Nov 28 17.
1. There are lots of immortals; giants, stormwings, griffins, basilisks, tauroses, coldfangs, dragons, centaurs, unicorns,
winged horses, winged apes, and what else?

( ) Ogres
( ) Duckmoles
( ) Marmosets
( ) Puffins


NEXT>

2. What is it that marks an animal as an immortal?

( ) Silver wings
( ) Golden wings
( ) Golden claws
( ) Silver claws


NEXT>

3. What is the name of the immortal that hunts for thieves?

( ) Dragon
( ) Stormwing
( ) Coldfang
( ) Hotfang


NEXT>

4. Which immortal knows every language there is and is extremely tall?

( ) Dragon
( ) Stormwing
( ) Basilisk
( ) Unicorn


NEXT>

5. Which immortal has steel wings?

( ) Dragon
( ) Basilisk
( ) Hurrok
( ) Stormwing


NEXT>

6. Which of these is not an immortal?

( ) Skysong
( ) Kitten
( ) Cloud
( ) Tkaa


NEXT>

7. Which of these is an immortal?

( ) Mindelan
( ) Arram
( ) Griffin
( ) Peachblossom


NEXT>

8. What animals are spidrens most like?

( ) Spiders and humans
( ) Eagles and coldfangs
( ) Spiders and horses
( ) Eagles and frogs


NEXT>

9. How do dragons speak?

( ) In both of those ways
( ) In hums and buzzes
( ) In whistles and clucks
( ) In neither of these ways


NEXT>

10. Finally, where do most immortals live?

( ) Realms of the dead
( ) Realms of the immortals
( ) Realms of the gods
( ) Realms of the inhuman


